  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The hypothesis is that adding the toothbrushing to the oral care with clorhexidine 0.12%
      could be reduce the incidence of ventilator-associated pneumonia due to that oral cavity may
      be an important reservoir of pathogens that could cause pneumonia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
